WEBVTT

00:02:25.180 --> 00:02:30.345
is a big, big step.

00:02:30.345 --> 00:02:35.997
But what to do with this privilege?

00:02:35.997 --> 00:02:39.952
Since I was a student, I wanted to open up

00:02:39.952 --> 00:02:42.595
better opportunities to other kids in Gando.

00:02:42.595 --> 00:02:45.510
I just wanted to use my skills and build a school.

00:02:45.510 --> 00:02:48.494
But how do you do it when you're still a student

00:02:48.494 --> 00:02:50.576
and you don't have money?

00:02:50.576 --> 00:02:53.078
Oh yes, I started to make drawings

00:02:53.078 --> 00:02:55.060
and asked for money.

00:02:55.060 --> 00:02:59.039
Fundraising was not an easy task.

00:02:59.039 --> 00:03:01.838
I even asked my classmates